{"tid":309332,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"（絲入）你地會唔會好易流眼淚","createTime":"2017-07-05T02:29:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-06T07:58:48.000Z","uid":110074,"like":29,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"880c20443bbf8ad6fb7f442e6ed6fd49a92e919d","tid":309332,"uid":110074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T02:29:32.000Z","msg":"有少少唔開心就會開始眼濕濕想流眼淚<br />\n男朋友次次都問我做咩又喊<br />\n但我覺得流眼淚唔同喊<br />\n流眼淚係純粹想流，可能係有野唔開心<br />\n覺得流完會舒服啲<br />\n但喊係有野好唔開心或者好嬲搞到要喊出聲先叫喊<br />\n有冇人明我呢種邏輯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n次次男朋友見到我啲眼淚都嫌我煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇辦法可以唔好咁易流眼淚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7576932fb894a19360620b70f18e6acc2b82ecde","tid":309332,"uid":110074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T02:32:10.000Z","msg":"定其實真係我咁懦弱先咁易流眼淚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b222a0b62cffbd33bf0926b587553c51d5948a7","tid":309332,"uid":88521,"like":14,"dislike":7,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T02:32:36.000Z","msg":"老實講 一個男人如果出面番工已經好攰 番到黎仲要見到個女人喊 真係覺得好煩同好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想抖下都唔得"},{"pid":"75df63cfa848e3bd2cae903e8a0eb09078865b2f","tid":309332,"uid":82457,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T02:33:54.000Z","msg":"平時堅強，對著愛情先特別軟弱。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利伸：巴打"},{"pid":"739ebc06b4b05fefe15c0cc4ce81e55a1471722e","tid":309332,"uid":83531,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T02:38:02.000Z","msg":"我明你想講咩 我都覺得流眼淚唔同喊<br />\n有時過一排覺得個人好攰 之後聽sad歌會流眼淚安慰下自己 覺得流完心情會好好多<br />\n而喊就真係勁唔開心頂唔順現況 喊完心情都唔會變好 只不過比我發洩左下"},{"pid":"2da71b89d9a3a1d57bab010362103c642657fff4","tid":309332,"uid":3852,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T02:42:49.000Z","msg":"水瓶座？<br />\n我都好易流<br />\n細個嗰陣俾人卑兩卑就眼濕濕<br />\n大嗰咗唔會但都幾眼淺吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f34800815f2d661878a8d6d202ddb3d9a6a2b7c","tid":309332,"uid":3852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T02:43:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>水瓶座？<br />\n我都好易流<br />\n細個嗰陣俾人<span style=\"color: red;\">睥</span>兩<span style=\"color: red;\">睥</span>就眼濕濕<br />\n大嗰咗唔會但都幾眼淺吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"836f80ca77c7c3b4032dca38d6e9b4aa14dee543","tid":309332,"uid":37005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T03:36:19.000Z","msg":"我都覺得兩樣係唔同 流眼淚本身冇任何煩惱但有情緒就會流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即係睇完條短片有情緒會流 但唔係本身唔開心"},{"pid":"b95eaecca69cc190fc2b759b17a7a2b70b7635f3","tid":309332,"uid":110074,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T03:36:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老實講 一個男人如果出面番工已經好攰 番到黎仲要見到個女人喊 真係覺得好煩同好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想抖下都唔得</blockquote><br />\n我都明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以佢一話我煩我就即刻道歉同埋自己收聲<br />\n其實往另一面諗<br />\n如果唔係佢嘅話我都唔會流眼淚<br />\n搞到我咁之後仲要話我煩其實我都好炆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人諗過我嘅感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"565f9f351e38cebf7cfe7b04a7de8a28e2e6d78f","tid":309332,"uid":110074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T03:38:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>平時堅強，對著愛情先特別軟弱。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利伸：巴打</blockquote><br />\n如果係巴，我會心生同情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平時堅強但對愛情軟弱嘅男人好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cad0afa665586b7058c92eda92f371685fdc98f5","tid":309332,"uid":110074,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T03:40:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我明你想講咩 我都覺得流眼淚唔同喊<br />\n有時過一排覺得個人好攰 之後聽sad歌會流眼淚安慰下自己 覺得流完心情會好好多<br />\n而喊就真係勁唔開心頂唔順現況 喊完心情都唔會變好 只不過比我發洩左下</blockquote><br />\n係啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n喊完心情唔會變好<br />\n男朋友成日話唔想氹我但其實根本唔洗佢氹<br />\n咁唔想見到我流眼淚咁我行開囉<br />\n過一陣自我回復完其實就冇事<br />\n係佢死都要走黎話我又喊個啲搞到我更炆更想喊"},{"pid":"da1d7dd5d44fe3a17e8a505e34dc3a1a41ca98c9","tid":309332,"uid":110074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T03:42:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>水瓶座？<br />\n我都好易流<br />\n細個嗰陣俾人<span style=\"color: red;\">睥</span>兩<span style=\"color: red;\">睥</span>就眼濕濕<br />\n大嗰咗唔會但都幾眼淺吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n唔係水瓶但超級眼淺<br />\n我以前唔係咁<br />\n係自從有段戀情好hurt日喊夜喊之後就好易喊<br />\n可能喊慣左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff79686a834f2c3c26d683075d2b7d7a7072d64a","tid":309332,"uid":110074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T03:43:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都覺得兩樣係唔同 流眼淚本身冇任何煩惱但有情緒就會流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即係睇完條短片有情緒會流 但唔係本身唔開心</blockquote><br />\n冇錯！我好易代入角色然後身同感受"},{"pid":"c644868e3a079e2c3fabdf2e90e02b6ad4164a71","tid":309332,"uid":11430,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T03:44:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>水瓶座？<br />\n我都好易流<br />\n細個嗰陣俾人卑兩卑就眼濕濕<br />\n大嗰咗唔會但都幾眼淺吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我女友都係水瓶座<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日喊，又易玻璃心發作"},{"pid":"4d2ecf0b6ce780478112a10a554b70e9b3a6b650","tid":309332,"uid":110074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T04:36:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>水瓶座？<br />\n我都好易流<br />\n細個嗰陣俾人卑兩卑就眼濕濕<br />\n大嗰咗唔會